  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate the safety and efficacy of inhaled Iloprost
      (Ventavis®) among adult Chinese patients with primary pulmonary hypertension, which is in
      compliance with Chinese SFDA regulation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
